29 (2) is committed against a member of a foster family home (as
30 defined in IC 35-31.5-2-139.3) by a person who is not a resident
31 of the foster family home if the person who committed the offense
32 is a relative of a person who lived in the foster family home at the
33 time of the offense.
34 (e) The offense described in subsection (c)(1) or (c)(2) is a Level 6
