32 fluid" means:
33 (1) blood;
34 (2) saliva;
35 (3) sputum;
36 (4) semen;
37 (5) vaginal secretions;
38 (6) human milk;
39 (7) urine;
40 (8) sweat;
41 (9) tears;
42 (10) any other liquid produced by the body; or
